{"tid":1446831,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"狗係圍魏救趙","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:20:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:42:35.000Z","uid":295099,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b675ceb458a5b79514c1003ef6d4e4fcbb9af760","tid":1446831,"uid":295099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:20:58.000Z","msg":"狗係刻意激發更多暴力，大家想報仇，可能會將焦點放喺點樣以暴易暴。<br />\n<br />\n但係機場先係我哋惟一嘅籌碼。唔排除狗係想減弱我哋機場嘅力量。<br />\n<br />\n但係正正，哩個時候我哋先係最需要加強機場嘅力量！狗畀咗好多粒子彈我哋。我哋要好好運用佢喺機場嘅文宣度。<br />\n<br />\n宜家可能好嬲，但係以暴易暴冇意思，除非你真係正面打得贏佢。<br />\n<br />\n愈憤怒，愈要冷靜。"},{"pid":"952fd25d07f8365ff6c9c9caea7d2e5baec72fcf","tid":1446831,"uid":286874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:21:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"36d619ac931adf52a66f8c3b73254960352c675f","tid":1446831,"uid":295099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"952fd25d07f8365ff6c9c9caea7d2e5baec72fcf","tid":1446831,"uid":286874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:21:32.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:22:20.000Z","msg":"多謝"},{"pid":"a1d2dac324676b3377b887c7c1b7c5578b75d810","tid":1446831,"uid":295099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:23:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e4390555a49704d6253940e423b7bf6dc16d1de3","tid":1446831,"uid":278205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:28:36.000Z","msg":"721。811"},{"pid":"63873292b373001f9f1aeba772cee48720ab5c18","tid":1446831,"uid":278205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:28:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f9be5ddf1247e2a48f79ca37ec6450a0a762c3c3","tid":1446831,"uid":259622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:29:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/z57whys0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Fz57whys0&d=rP1lJsqA2sO3Td0%2BA1LJ506%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=db6818ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">htt